Communications Plus & Third Party Configurations:
To get our campus set up for communications, I need to create accounts with sendGrid and Twilio, and then configure communications to work with them.
Steps:
First click on Navigation bar under Core click into system administration and Under Data Privacy click Product Installs and Sign in.

Data Integrity:
Steps:
In core--> Campus-wide definitions--> Contact definitions
Sort EMails by priority order by clicking on Edit, make chnages and update it.
Sending out communications:
Search for person, under Person name we can see all details.
